# reopen.persona — changed-answer-reopens-dependents (REQ-C1.2). The design
# decision is answered, then the upstream level is CHANGED, which reopens and
# re-asks the dependent decision; the final sign-off reflects the NEW answers,
# not the stale ones. Turn map: 1 level(novice), 2 decision(alpha),
# 3 level-restate(expert -> changed), 4 reopened decision(beta), 5 sign-off.
expertise=novice
answer.1=novice
answer.2=option-alpha
answer.3=expert
answer.4=option-beta
answer.5=record-approval
